<emphasis id="3592EA9F0B6016517C3CF84323DAF83F" bold="true" box="[1129,1152,1921,1942]" pageId="16" pageNumber="121">D.</emphasis>
Branch with leaves, immature schizocarps and flower bud. 
<emphasis id="3592EA9F0B60165179F5F86726ECF813" bold="true" box="[416,438,1957,1978]" pageId="16" pageNumber="121">E.</emphasis>
