<emphasis id="3592EA9F0B6016517929F7D026ADF78F" box="[380,503,2065,2087]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="121">K. Hagelund</emphasis>
2228, HAS) and J–O by Luís Funez.
</paragraph>
